item.title: About
item.description: I am: ambient musician erstwhile radio deejay nonprofit worker occasional activist habitual researcher amateur technologist athletics aficionado native midwesterner Feel free to reach out though the channels listed on the Home page. I’m also happy to communicate using PGP <3 ~ This website is self-hosted using Hugo, Caddy, and Armbian. I recently experimented with solar powering it. The logo is an edited Open Doodle.
